Lec 1:
Writing Simple Unit test
-Here we wrote the add function then performed the test
-to perform unit test, the def function should start with test ie test_add_numbers
-run the test command
-----docker-compose run app sh -c "python manage.py test"

Lec 2:
Performing a test using Test Driven development
-With test Driven development, you write the test then write the function there after
-Here you know your tests work well